Class WifiP2pNetworkInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.wifi.p2p.WifiP2pNetworkInfo

    public class WifiP2pNetworkInfo
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Provides detailed information about the Wi-Fi P2P network.

    You can use WifiP2pController#requestP2pInfo(int, WifiP2pCallback) to obtain information about the Wi-Fi P2P network.
